The paper deals with signal and image processing, specifically the decomposition of the 2D nonseparable linear canonical transform. This makes it likely to fall under the sub-categories of Information Theory (cs.IT), Signal Processing (cs.SP), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Multimedia (cs.MM), and Numerical Analysis (cs.NA).
